definitions.definition: An ungainly , dull , or stupid person ; someone who is lazy , disrespectful , and/or whose beliefs and philosophies clash with those of another.
A large , muscular , stupid man , especially an athlete .
examples: Gary was a hulking meathead who, when he wasn't playing football, was either hunting, fishing or getting drunk and rowdy in some topless bar.

definitions.definition: A member of the Canadian Forces Military Police .
